Fetch PCA Dimensions and Cellular Metadata

Fetch PCA Dimensions and Cellular Metadata

fetchPCAData(object, ...)

# S4 method for seurat
fetchPCAData(object)

Arguments

object

Object.
...

Additional arguments (for the S4 generic definition).

Value

data.frame of PCA points and metadata for each cell.

See also

Seurat::PCAPlot().

Other PCA Utilities: plotPCA

Examples

load(system.file(
    file.path("extdata", "seurat.rda"),
    package = "bcbioSingleCell"))

# seurat
fetchPCAData(seurat) %>% glimpse()
